4 SYNOPSIS:
5 Under existing law, "gross income" is defined
6 for the purpose of state income tax. Also, existing law
7 exempts certain amounts from the calculation of gross
8 income.
9 This bill would exclude payments made under
10 certain Medicaid Home and Community-Based Services
11 Waiver programs to an individual care provider from
12 being included in the calculation of gross income.
13
14
15 A BILL
16 TO BE ENTITLED
17 AN ACT
18
19 Relating to gross income; to amend Section 40-18-14,
20 Code of Alabama 1975; to exclude payments to individual care
21 providers under certain Medicaid Home and Community-Based
22 Services Waiver programs from gross income.
23 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
